description: Manage and configure Azure Firewall application rule collections.

commands.name: az network firewall application-rule collection delete
commands.summary: Delete an Azure Firewall application rule collection.
commands.syntax:
az network firewall application-rule collection delete [--collection-name]
                                                       [--firewall-name]
                                                       [--ids]
                                                       [--resource-group]
                                                       [--subscription]

commands.name: az network firewall application-rule collection list
commands.summary: List Azure Firewall application rule collections.
commands.syntax:
az network firewall application-rule collection list --firewall-name
                                                     --resource-group

commands.name: az network firewall application-rule collection show
commands.summary: Get the details of an Azure Firewall application rule collection.
commands.syntax:
az network firewall application-rule collection show [--collection-name]
                                                     [--firewall-name]
                                                     [--ids]
                                                     [--resource-group]
                                                     [--subscription]
